{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Ban selling disposable barbecues without a stand, to prevent grass damage",
        "additional_details": "Parks, natural green spaces and nature reserves are being damaged by people using disposable barbecues with little to no thought of the grass being burnt and long term damage caused.",
        "background": "The Government should make it illegal to sell barbecues without a permanently attached stand for them to be used on. This could be a fold out stand or legs. This would ensure manufacturers stop producing disposable barbecues without such stands.",
